# type: textblock
#: ../../lib/Locale/Po4a/Sgml.pm:136
msgid ""
"The problem is that I have to \"protect\" the conditional inclusions (ie, "
"the C<E<lt>! [ %foo [> and C<]]E<gt>> stuff) from nsgmls. Otherwise nsgmls "
